    <stitle>DT/DTA-466 Diesel Engine Service (1990) - MANIFOLDS - EXHAUST MANIFOLD PIPING</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="2">
        <title>EXHAUST MANIFOLD PIPING</title>
        <para>Refer to
            <emph type="bold">Figure
                <hotlnk xrefid="ef4150302">3.2</hotlnk>
            </emph>
            for component locations for the DTA 466 4000 and 7000 Series (was 1900 and 2100 Series).
        </para>
        <para>Refer to
            <emph type="bold">Figure
                <hotlnk xrefid="ef4150303">3.3</hotlnk>
            </emph>
            for component locations for the DTA 466 (2000, 2500 or 2600 Series applications only.
        </para>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>2000 or 2500 AND 2600 SERIES APPLICATIONS REQUIRE THE CHASSIS MOUNTED INTERCOOLER TO BE MOUNTED
                    TRANSVERSELY, AS SHOWN IN FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef4150303">3.3</hotlnk>. THE 4000 AND 7000 (WAS 1900 AND 2100) SERIES APPLICATIONS
                    REQUIRE THE INTERCOOLER TO BE MOUNTED IN THE UPRIGHT POSITION, AS SHOWN IN FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef4150302">3.2</hotlnk>. INTERCOOLERS ARE NOT INTERCHANGEABLE.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>THE INTERCOOLER (3) AND CONNECTING HARDWARE (1, 2 &#38; 4-7) USED ON DTA ENGINES IS CHASSIS
                    MOUNTED. REFER TO THE APPROPRIATE CHASSIS MANUAL AND PARTS CATALOG FOR DETAILED INFORMATION.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <figure id="ef4150302" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="cg11853" filename="../figcg1/CG11853.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 3.2 Major Component Location (DTA-466) 4000 and 7000 (Was 1900 &#38; 2100) Series</caption>
        </figure>
        <figure id="ef4150303" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic id="cg14512" filename="../figcg1/CG14512.webp" type="webp"/>
            <caption>Figure 3.3 Air Intake Piping (DTA 466) 2000 or 2500 Series Applications Only.</caption>
            <calloutgroup>
                <callout1 type="arabic">1. Mounting Bracket</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">2. Turbo To Intercooler Pipe (Hot Side)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">3. Chassis Mounted Air-To-Air Intercooler</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">4. Intercooler To Intake Manifold Pipe (Cold Side)</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">5. Spring Clamp</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">6. Intercooler Hose</callout1>
                <callout1 type="arabic">7. Worm Clamp</callout1>
            </calloutgroup>
        </figure>
